{"tid":1181149,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★充滿信心狂掃樓？投資客唔睇樓　一筆過付538萬購屯門市廣場兩房收租","createTime":"2019-06-01T11:24:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-01T12:02:06.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d1352c54974516ef648d228767c03f288232040b","tid":1181149,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T11:24:25.000Z","msg":"但有投資者繼續入市「買磚頭」。祥益袁思賢稱，日前屯門市廣場錄得一宗區外投資客「不睇樓」成交個案。<br />\n<br />\n她表示，成交單位為4座中層F室，實用面積392呎，兩房一廳，由於單位連租約，故未能視察內籠，買家僅參考單位的相片，加上原業主擴大議價空間，減價12萬，買家遂便決定「不睇樓」，以538萬並「一筆過」付款購入上址<span style=\"color: red;\">作長線投資收租之用</span>，實用呎價為13,724元。<br />\n<br />\n袁思賢表示，該單位若作投資收租，現時市值租金大約為1.2萬元，租金回報率為2.7厘；另外原業主於2013年以約300萬購入單位，是次轉手帳面獲利約高達238萬<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2%E6%A8%93%E5%B8%82/334939/%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E5%AE%A2%E5%94%94%E7%9D%87%E6%A8%93-%E4%B8%80%E7%AD%86%E9%81%8E%E4%BB%98538%E8%90%AC%E8%B3%BC%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E5%B8%82%E5%BB%A3%E5%A0%B4%E5%85%A9%E6%88%BF%E6%94%B6%E7%A7%9F-%E5%9B%9E%E5%A0%B1%E7%8E%872-7%E5%8E%98\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2594%25A2%25E6%25A8%2593%25E5%25B8%2582%2F334939%2F%25E6%258A%2595%25E8%25B3%2587%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E5%2594%2594%25E7%259D%2587%25E6%25A8%2593-%25E4%25B8%2580%25E7%25AD%2586%25E9%2581%258E%25E4%25BB%2598538%25E8%2590%25AC%25E8%25B3%25BC%25E5%25B1%25AF%25E9%2596%2580%25E5%25B8%2582%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E5%2585%25A9%25E6%2588%25BF%25E6%2594%25B6%25E7%25A7%259F-%25E5%259B%259E%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E7%258E%25872-7%25E5%258E%2598&d=77sZY8L1Q3njiwGc8u9yTjrpXFO54mr1mpDNnesGdkc%3D&h=5e008e0c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2%E6%A8%93%E5%B8%82/334939/%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E5%AE%A2%E5%94%94%E7%9D%87%E6%A8%93-%E4%B8%80%E7%AD%86%E9%81%8E%E4%BB%98538%E8%90%AC%E8%B3%BC%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E5%B8%82%E5%BB%A3%E5%A0%B4%E5%85%A9%E6%88%BF%E6%94%B6%E7%A7%9F-%E5%9B%9E%E5%A0%B1%E7%8E%872-7%E5%8E%98</a>"},{"pid":"fb6fae9509696fac3f90cf1da0e755704